{"id":193,"date":"2024-06-28T13:02:38","date_gmt":"2024-06-28T13:02:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/lighthq.com.ng\/ace\/?page_id=193"},"modified":"2024-09-12T16:48:07","modified_gmt":"2024-09-12T16:48:07","slug":"advocacy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/our-work\/advocacy\/","title":{"rendered":"Research and Advocacy"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"193\" class=\"elementor elementor-193\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66d011a6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"66d011a6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;gradient&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1f405806 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1f405806\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-525f12e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"525f12e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Research and Advocacy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4ca51087 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4ca51087\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4cf1f786 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4cf1f786\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e359bc0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2e359bc0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3364ae9c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3364ae9c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-65a079bf e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"65a079bf\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40a7edf5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"40a7edf5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1f9be223 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1f9be223\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1440\" height=\"960\" src=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Research-and-Advocacy-SSK-1621.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-30080\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Research-and-Advocacy-SSK-1621.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Research-and-Advocacy-SSK-1621-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Research-and-Advocacy-SSK-1621-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Research-and-Advocacy-SSK-1621-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-14391f99 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"14391f99\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-47a5a4d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"47a5a4d7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have conducted and published research on experiences of out-of-school boys and girls, as well as beneficiary experiences of alternative forms of education. Our research has been published in academic journals. We have also published and disseminated policy briefs highlighting the state of girl child education in Borno, Adamawa and Kano states.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our advocacy efforts have facilitated the domestication of the Child Rights Act in Adamawa state.\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So far, ACE Charity has collaborated with other NGOs to develop an education manifesto with input from community and religious leaders, local CSOs, schoolteachers and girls in Adamawa state. ACE Charity developed an impactful documentary showcasing education challenges among out-of-school and in-school girls in Adamawa.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The education manifesto and documentary were used as an advocacy tool to secure the commitment of flag bearers and elected government officials to providing free, safe, and quality education.\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a954ab4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a954ab4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In partnership with Malala Fund, ACE Charity is advocating for the development and implementation of Gender Responsive Education Sector Plans in Oyo State.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2179391 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2179391\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3460c8c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3460c8c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c414730 elementor-widget elementor-widget-jkit_dual_button\" data-id=\"c414730\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"jkit_dual_button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div  class=\"jeg-elementor-kit jkit-dual-button jeg_module___68e8f1b2e6985\" ><div class=\"jkit-dual-button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/US902EohhO0?si=aTeRU-nm6ViTcnVB\" class=\"jkit-dual-btn jkit-dual-button-one\" target=\"_blank\">Watch our Documentary<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1TxZcEQLac9qMjNFOqUHz7S7WaB64uuZR\/view?usp=drive_link\" class=\"jkit-dual-btn jkit-dual-button-two\" target=\"_blank\">Read Education Manifesto<\/a><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Research and Advocacy We have conducted and published research on experiences of out-of-school boys and girls, as well as beneficiary experiences of alternative forms of education. Our research has been published in academic journals. We have also published and disseminated policy briefs highlighting the state of girl child education in Borno, Adamawa and Kano states. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":160,"menu_order":4,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"elementor_header_footer","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-193","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/acecharityafrica.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/193","target